scripts to generate the papers

1. create a template paper for topic <topic>

	bash scripts/mktemplate <topic>

2. create infrastructure files 

	a) enter all the paper topics into the file common/paperlist

	b) run the all scripts using 

		bash scripts/mkall

	   or run them individually

		bash scripts/mkbibresources
		bash scripts/mkmakefile
		bash scripts/mkpackages
		bash scripts/mkpapers

